feat: v1.0.0 — full platform evolution (5 phases)

Phase 1 — UX Quick Wins:
- Remove file_id deletion after submit (photo persists 24h in Redis)
- Add action_keyboard after every result (no more dead ends)
- Add error_keyboard to all error/timeout messages
- Shorten result templates for rating/dating/cv/emoji

Phase 2 — Mode Switching + Loop:
- Add action: handlers for mode switching without re-upload
- Add loop:/restyle: handlers for iterative refinement
- Add personality styles (friendly/confident/charismatic for dating, corporate/startup/creative for CV)
- Store last_gen state in Redis for retry

Phase 3 — Architecture Cleanup:
- Create src/prompts/image_gen.py (centralized image gen prompts)
- Add build_image_prompt to PromptEngine
- Split pipeline.execute() into _preprocess/_analyze/_generate_image/_finalize
- Add close() to LLMProvider/ImageGenProvider/StorageProvider ABCs
- Remove dead code (AnalyzeRequest, ShareRequest schemas)
- Fix enhancement.provider to use actual class name

Phase 4 — Monetization:
- Add image_credits to User model (default 1)
- Add CreditTransaction table + Alembic migration 003
- Add context column to Task model
- Worker deducts credits on successful generation
- Skip image gen when credits exhausted (upgrade_prompt flag)
- Add upgrade_keyboard with pricing tiers
- Add buy: callback handler (placeholder)

Phase 5 — Performance:
- Redis Pub/Sub for task completion (worker publishes, bot subscribes)
- Merge NSFW check into analysis prompt (eliminate double LLM call)
- Auto-retry failed tasks once (skip user-facing errors)
- Bump version to 1.0.0
